{"tid":1853271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[睇完#1先好問] 網購外科口罩集中區62","createTime":"2020-01-31T01:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T01:23:17.000Z","uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"df371906b594306fd7da965de2d0ea58a2e8e737","tid":1853271,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。旅客在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢獨立健康、財務及其他的專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到口臭，屌你老母閪<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問得唔得嘅，最少睇曬前2/3個po嘅圖<br />\n <br />\n做開團團長嘅，求下你，你開個tg,wts gp出嚟畀人join,夠數咪關link囉</span><br />\n <br />\niris plaza,yodobashi冇日本卡9成9cut<br />\nDokodemo好多會cut，但有成功個案<br />\n美國Amazon有分直送香港/國內送再集運<br />\n你一共要畀3舊錢，件貨/國內運費/集運<br />\n所有風險自行承擔<br />\n <br />\n個盒寫撚齊曬PFE VFE BFE99%標準，你都仲可以問得唔得嘅，我屌你老母閪，post唔撚係咁推<br />\n冇寫嘅，Google下囉，有邊個唔係Google 個spec，Google間公司，Google第2間舖頭有冇寫spec<br />\n使唔使我買埋送到你屋企幫你戴埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母臭化閪，你再問我再屌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好買太多 到時禁運真係攬炒就一鑊熟</span><br />\n <br />\n常見問題睇呢度<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buyandship.today/blog/2020/01/29/%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-amazon-rakuten-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-lazada-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buyandship.today%2Fblog%2F2020%2F01%2F29%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-amazon-rakuten-%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B-lazada-%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=b67f3deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.buyandship.today/blog/2020/01/29/%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-amazon-rakuten-%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B-lazada-%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPv5LzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPv5LzF.png&h=37388f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"521c2cb87ca8aa556bc1bc0fdc484ef56e02154a","tid":1853271,"uid":50421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2e7fdc228cdf0bb8f0b6b8428387cfc9676522","tid":1853271,"uid":147941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"521c2cb87ca8aa556bc1bc0fdc484ef56e02154a","tid":1853271,"uid":50421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20fd91bd55b28d91164eae0888df6581b46f374","tid":1853271,"uid":112688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2368acb6dab3c3e1aedb5d32302dc38752f794","tid":1853271,"uid":101914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfcaa67eaa980213b45f1c5310b92b30f6fd414","tid":1853271,"uid":50889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2368acb6dab3c3e1aedb5d32302dc38752f794","tid":1853271,"uid":101914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T01:15:11.000Z","msg"